Sentencas: High-performance (La,Sr)MnO3 (LSM) cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated by the ion impregnation of oxygen ion conducting Gd-doped CeO2 (GDC) oxide.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The microstructure of the GDC-impregnated LSM electrode was characterized by the uniform dispersion of very fine GDC particles in the LSM porous framework.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The particle size of the impregnated GDC phase was in the range of 100-200 nm.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Uniform distribution of the nanosized ionic conducting GDC phase significantly enhanced the electrode activities for the O-2 reduction reaction.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the case of the 5.8 mg cm(-2) GDC-impregnated LSM electrode, electrode polarization resistance was 0.21 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C, 56 times lower than that of the pure LSM at the same temperature.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: GDC-impregnated LSM electrode showed lower activation energy and low reaction order with respect to the partial pressure of oxygen, as compared to that on the pure LSM electrodes.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that GDC impregnation has significant electrocatalytic effect on the O-2 reduction reactions on the LSM electrodes.
Titulo: Fabrication and performance of GDC-impregnated (La,Sr)MnO3 cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
